import React, { useContext } from 'react'
import { NumberHandContext } from '../../contexts/NumberHandContext'
import { Container, Objective, Hand } from './styles'
import { Body, Main, TextArea, N1, TextInput, Button } from '../styles'


export default function NumberHand() {


  const { } = useContext(NumberHandContext)


  return (
    <Body>
      <Main>
        <N1>
          <Text>{number1} </Text>
        </N1>

        <TextArea>
          <Container>
            <Objective>Objetivo do jogo</Objective>

            <Hand
              source={require('../../../images/mao0.png')}
              resizeMode="cover"
            />

          </Container>
          <TextInput value={number2} onChangeText={(text) => { setNumber2(text) }} />
        </TextArea>

        <Button title="Verificar" onPress={handleClick} />
      </Main>
    </Body>
  )
}
